#2402
The Memebers Only Wing~
As you enter, you pass a doorwarden that checks your
identification as a member of Gondor before letting you pass. 
Obviously this is a members only area.  The ceiling here is somewhat
lower, less grand, but you definitely feel more at home.  In the
corners stand braziers, burning incense and providing a dim
illumination to the place.  The dim illumination is also a welcome
respite to your senses after the brightness of the entryway.  The
walls in here are covered with tapestries and rugs of all makes, and
are very pleasing to look at.  Several benches line the walls and
floor, giving the weary a place to sit and relax.  To the north you
hear a couple murmurs now and then and you see a woman awlking
around, stooping, whispering things, and then walking on.  To the
west are several large chests, full of equipment for members.  
~
