#2403
The Healer~
The room you are in is lit by a dim light, but it is more than
enough to see by.  The floor is covered in soft pillows for resting
on, and a few servants bring in cold drinks and snacks to those
relaxing here.  In the back corner you notice a mat with a staff
leaning on the wall over it and a traveling cloak very precisely
folded over it.  Your eyes then travel around the room, and you
notice a young, beautiful woman, glowing slightly, walking around the
room.  Periodically she stops to murmer in someone's ear, and she
glows brighter for a moment, then she smiles and walks on.  You look
back to that corner where her posessions are and notice a slight
bulge underneath the mat, where she is presumably storing the cash
she collects from her services....  
~
